strInstructions: 1. Prepare all fresh ingredients. 2. Marinate the protein with spices and herbs for 30 minutes. 3. Heat oil in a large pan or wok. 4. Sauté onions, garlic, and ginger until aromatic. 5. Add the main base ingredients and cook until tender. 6. Season with salt, pepper, and secret sauces. 7. Garnish with fresh herbs and serve hot with side dishes. Enjoy your Tuscan Polenta!
